title: Lord Bourath Arceuus

properties.name: description
properties.value: Lord Bourath Arceuus was the leader of the Arceuus House at the time of the signing of the royal accord of twill and advised it's creation.[1]

content:
Lord Bourath Arceuus was the leader of the Arceuus House at the time of the signing of the royal accord of twill and advised it's creation.[1]
